But it wasn't looking to
see if they were harmed.

247
00:28:00.896 --> 00:28:04.770
- My cousin. she said
she had a miscarriage

248
00:28:04.813 --> 00:28:07.511
and a friend of mine. she
did have a miscarriage.

249
00:28:07.555 --> 00:28:09.078
- [Reporter] And this was all

250
00:28:09.122 --> 00:28:09.949
in this area where
they're spraying?

251
00:28:09.992 --> 00:28:11.602
- Yeah.

252
00:28:11.646 --> 00:28:14.867
- The women have lived in areas

253
00:28:14.910 --> 00:28:17.043
that have been sprayed
very close to their homes.

254
00:28:17.086 --> 00:28:19.393
Many of us have
gravity-feed water systems.

255
00:28:19.436 --> 00:28:21.221
And the dates that
they were sprayed

256
00:28:21.264 --> 00:28:23.527
are really amazing
because all of the areas

257
00:28:23.571 --> 00:28:26.139
were sprayed within a month
before the miscarriage.

258
00:28:26.182 --> 00:28:28.010
- And it was very stunning

259
00:28:29.533 --> 00:28:32.536
that they would spray an
area and within a month

260
00:28:32.580 --> 00:28:35.801
the miscarriage
rate--what they called

261
00:28:35.844 --> 00:28:39.935
the spontaneous abortion
rate--would skyrocket.

262
00:28:41.023 --> 00:28:43.460
according to the hospital data.

263
00:28:53.427 --> 00:28:56.909
- Between my husband and I
and our nurse practitioner.

264
00:28:56.952 --> 00:29:01.696
we delivered between 100
and 150 children a year...

265
00:29:04.264 --> 00:29:06.875
seeing a larger number
of birth defects

266
00:29:06.919 --> 00:29:09.356
than we would've expected.

267
00:29:09.399 --> 00:29:12.925
We saw a number of
congenital hearts.

268
00:29:14.665 --> 00:29:19.496
And I think it was 1978. I
delivered an anencephalic child.

269
00:29:21.237 --> 00:29:24.719
That's a child that doesn't
have basically the normal brain.

270
00:29:26.199 --> 00:29:27.722
In my lifetime of
delivering babies.

271
00:29:27.766 --> 00:29:29.506
I would not expect
ever to see one.

272
00:29:30.943 --> 00:29:33.423
And about a year later.

273
00:29:33.467 --> 00:29:37.123
we delivered a second
anencephalic child.

274
00:29:37.166 --> 00:29:40.604
Those odds were
just astronomical

275
00:29:40.648 --> 00:29:42.781
that a small practice like ours

276
00:29:42.824 --> 00:29:44.739
would have two
anencephalic children.

277
00:29:46.349 --> 00:29:48.787
All of these
chemicals are suspect.

278
00:29:48.830 --> 00:29:51.311
We know in animals that
they cause birth defects.

279
00:29:51.354 --> 00:29:53.443
Why are we using them in humans?

280
00:29:56.055 --> 00:29:58.797
It made me realize that
there was something going on

281
00:30:00.581 --> 00:30:03.149
and the something
that I was aware of

282
00:30:03.192 --> 00:30:06.500
was broadcast spraying
of herbicides.

283
00:30:06.543 --> 00:30:11.548
At that point. it was mainly
2.4-D over our water supplies

284
00:30:12.941 --> 00:30:15.161
because we drink surface
water at the coast.

285
00:30:16.727 --> 00:30:19.948
[ominous tones ]

286
00:30:52.502 --> 00:30:54.461
[camera snaps]

287
00:30:57.507 --> 00:31:01.337
- Down below me is a
dam and a water supply.

288
00:31:01.381 --> 00:31:04.123
If this camera shows it.
there's the helicopter

289
00:31:04.166 --> 00:31:06.038
on the ridge right
there by the trees.

290
00:31:06.081 --> 00:31:08.692
So we're gonna be
spraying right below it.

291
00:31:08.736 --> 00:31:10.607
Crazy!

292
00:31:10.651 --> 00:31:13.915
That whole unit over there
is dead. dead. dead. dead

