00:31:13.959 --> 00:31:15.264
and they're spraying
more chemicals on it

294
00:31:15.308 --> 00:31:17.266
right now as we speak.

295
00:31:17.310 --> 00:31:19.225
I gotta hold this low because

296
00:31:19.268 --> 00:31:21.531
right over there is the
honcho of the forest.

297
00:31:23.272 --> 00:31:26.188
So basically we
dropped 1160 gallons

298
00:31:27.494 --> 00:31:29.061
into this right here

299
00:31:30.584 --> 00:31:32.455
and it is. I'm gonna
show you real quick.

300
00:31:34.153 --> 00:31:39.114
it's gonna go basically right
down into that watershed

301
00:31:40.550 --> 00:31:42.901
and the unit's already
de-weeded anyways.

302
00:31:42.944 --> 00:31:44.554
I don't know why they did that.

303
00:31:45.642 --> 00:31:46.774
And here's the reservoir.

304
00:31:46.817 --> 00:31:48.123
I'm down here at the reservoir.

305
00:31:50.343 --> 00:31:52.214
And we're gonna go spray

306
00:31:53.694 --> 00:31:55.000
on the other side of
the reservoir now.

307
00:31:55.043 --> 00:31:56.610
Both sides of the watershed.

308
00:31:59.613 --> 00:32:02.268
[Darryl coughs]

309
00:32:03.312 --> 00:32:05.271
My throat is burning.

310
00:32:16.891 --> 00:32:20.721
- The kids were involved in
the whole herbicide battle.

311
00:32:23.028 --> 00:32:25.160
They were helping
write the newsletters

312
00:32:25.204 --> 00:32:28.207
and draw the pictures
and help with signs.

313
00:32:31.471 --> 00:32:34.648
There's the poster
that Daphne made.

314
00:32:34.691 --> 00:32:36.606
She did that when
she was about 11.

315
00:32:39.174 --> 00:32:41.872
They were right in
the thick of it.

316
00:32:45.833 --> 00:32:48.096
We had like five minutes
to come up with a name

317
00:32:48.140 --> 00:32:53.145
for this group: Citizens
Against Toxic Sprays. CATS.

318
00:32:54.973 --> 00:32:58.237
It wasn't the most imaginative
name but it worked. I guess.

319
00:32:59.238 --> 00:33:01.022
Hi.
- Hi. Carol.

320
00:33:01.066 --> 00:33:04.765
- And it wasn't until
basically CATS was formed

321
00:33:04.808 --> 00:33:09.117
and started questioning it
with filing a court action

322
00:33:09.161 --> 00:33:12.860
and then it suddenly
got some attention and

323
00:33:13.948 --> 00:33:15.776
there was a lot of pushback

324
00:33:15.819 --> 00:33:20.346
from the chemical companies
and the timber companies.

325
00:33:20.389 --> 00:33:22.783
- Chemicals are
being used as a means

326
00:33:22.826 --> 00:33:26.482
of achieving environmental
goals. really.

327
00:33:28.876 --> 00:33:32.880
The attack is not scientific.
it's purely emotional.

328
00:33:32.923 --> 00:33:37.058
The public does not understand
and we unfortunately

329
00:33:37.102 --> 00:33:40.757
haven't successfully
communicated to
the public as yet.

330
00:33:40.801 --> 00:33:43.804
Take 2.4.5-T for example.

331
00:33:43.847 --> 00:33:46.589
2.4.5-T is about as
toxic as aspirin.

332
00:33:49.636 --> 00:33:52.378
The safety factor in
the use of 2.4.5-T

333
00:33:52.421 --> 00:33:56.077
is far greater than the safety
factors in use of aspirin.

334
00:33:56.121 --> 00:33:58.036
Now does the public
understand that?

335
00:34:06.653 --> 00:34:08.394
- [Carol] Documents disappearing

336
00:34:08.437 --> 00:34:11.179
is a common thing I think
in this whole story.

337
00:34:14.748 --> 00:34:16.532
Susan Swift's health study

338
00:34:16.576 --> 00:34:19.405
that she was doing of
everybody in this valley...

339
00:34:22.147 --> 00:34:25.106
she had done door-to-door survey

340
00:34:25.150 --> 00:34:28.414
of peoples' health and the
children's health and animals.

341
00:34:28.457 --> 00:34:31.156
anything that people
could report about

342
00:34:33.027 --> 00:34:35.986
and her house getting broken
into and this health study.

343
00:34:36.030 --> 00:34:39.686
all the data she had
collected. it was gone.

344
00:34:43.646 --> 00:34:45.431
- I was just taking information

345
00:34:45.474 --> 00:34:46.954
and gathered the data together

346
00:34:46.997 --> 00:34:50.218
and I created a
questionnaire to go

347
00:34:50.262 --> 00:34:54.048
and I interviewed every home
up and down Five Rivers Road.

348
00:34:54.092 --> 00:34:55.571
There was an enormous amount

349
00:34:55.615 --> 00:34:59.532
of small tumors
and miscarriages.

350
00:34:59.575 --> 00:35:02.752
Right after that. my box of

351
00:35:02.796 --> 00:35:05.538
documented forms
disappeared out of my house.

352
00:35:07.627 --> 00:35:10.934
The board members of
Citizens Against Toxic Sprays

353
00:35:10.978 --> 00:35:13.372
were going to Eugene
over the mountain

354
00:35:13.415 --> 00:35:15.113
taking these Forest
Service roads.

355
00:35:15.156 --> 00:35:17.332
just going straight up
and over the mountain.

356
00:35:17.376 --> 00:35:19.856
all gravel little logging roads.

357
00:35:19.900 --> 00:35:24.426
and we were being
followed by a shiny sedan

358
00:35:24.470 --> 00:35:26.385
with guys in suits.

359
00:35:26.428 --> 00:35:28.822
And that was pretty bizarre.

360
00:35:28.865 --> 00:35:32.521
[low. ominous tones]

361
00:35:35.785 --> 00:35:38.048
- One Saturday morning
when my husband

362
00:35:38.092 --> 00:35:41.008
was making rounds
at the hospital.

363
00:35:41.051 --> 00:35:44.838
two fellows in suits
showed up at my front door

364
00:35:46.622 --> 00:35:50.017
and said they wanted to
talk about the herbicides.

365
00:35:50.060 --> 00:35:52.150
And I said that was fine.

366
00:35:52.193 --> 00:35:54.152
My two children
were running around

367
00:35:54.195 --> 00:35:55.675
very happily playing.

368
00:35:57.198 --> 00:35:58.721
They didn't really say
where they were from.

369
00:36:00.506 --> 00:36:02.551
I said. "Come on in.
have a cup of coffee."

370
00:36:02.595 --> 00:36:05.293
Because I had had a
number of reporters

371
00:36:05.337 --> 00:36:09.950
and other people show up.
And then when they said.

372
00:36:09.993 --> 00:36:13.345
"Do you know at all times
where your children are?"

373
00:36:15.173 --> 00:36:17.697
I realized that I didn't.

374
00:36:19.177 --> 00:36:23.093
And I said it was time
to end the interview

375
00:36:23.137 --> 00:36:27.359
because it was clearly a threat
against me and my children.

376
00:36:32.668 --> 00:36:34.888
And it worked. I'm done.

377
00:36:36.672 --> 00:36:40.720
- [Bruce] A van that had dark
tinted windows on both sides

378
00:36:40.763 --> 00:36:44.245
suddenly showed up outside
