00:40:09.929 --> 00:40:13.280
studies in Idaho of
roadside spray workers

433
00:40:13.323 --> 00:40:17.806
that showed deformed sperm
after the spray season.

434
00:40:19.286 --> 00:40:22.637
- So we put together
an information packet

435
00:40:22.681 --> 00:40:25.161
and then they could use
that information to take

436
00:40:25.205 --> 00:40:29.557
their own actions and file
their own cases. whatever.

