00:40:47.749 --> 00:40:50.143
the chemical companies
and the timber companies

441
00:40:50.186 --> 00:40:53.189
that number one. there's
nothing wrong with the sprays

442
00:40:53.233 --> 00:40:57.280
and number two. these people
are just the lunatic fringe.

443
00:40:59.848 --> 00:41:01.589
They convinced the
loggers or some

444
00:41:01.633 --> 00:41:03.504
of them anyway that
they were gonna all

445
00:41:03.548 --> 00:41:07.377
be out of work if they
couldn't use the herbicides.

446
00:41:17.475 --> 00:41:21.827
- The house was on fire when
