447
00:41:21.870 --> 00:41:23.481
The house was totally in flames.

448
00:41:24.873 --> 00:41:26.440
Patrick said he stopped her.

449
00:41:26.484 --> 00:41:28.268
that she grabbed a knife
off his belt and started

450
00:41:28.311 --> 00:41:31.793
running up the hill and he
just grabbed her and held her.

451
00:41:33.229 --> 00:41:36.232
And he felt sure
that Carol was gonna

452
00:41:36.276 --> 00:41:38.887
try to take her own
life that night.

453
00:41:43.718 --> 00:41:46.504
The Van Strum
children were gone...

454
00:41:52.684 --> 00:41:55.077
And we all crumbled. we all
just couldn't believe it.

455
00:42:00.909 --> 00:42:03.521
- The firefighters
said it was arson.

456
00:42:16.621 --> 00:42:20.276
It's hard to talk about
it. I just can't really.

457
00:42:38.730 --> 00:42:41.602
They had done the absolute
worst thing anybody

458
00:42:41.646 --> 00:42:46.346
could do to me and they
couldn't do anymore.

459
00:42:50.263 --> 00:42:52.570
Okay everybody. who's hungry?

460
00:42:53.658 --> 00:42:55.268
Yes. you want some brekker.

461
00:42:55.311 --> 00:42:56.965
The animals were still here.

462
00:42:57.009 --> 00:43:00.012
I think that's what
