to do nothing but produce

482
00:47:39.769 --> 00:47:41.859
Agent Orange and other chemicals
for the war in Vietnam.

483
00:47:43.338 --> 00:47:44.905
And they knew that the
more they produced.

484
00:47:44.949 --> 00:47:46.037
the more money they would make.

485
00:47:46.080 --> 00:47:48.126
So they. in order to

486
00:47:49.910 --> 00:47:52.130
deliver as much as they could
as quickly as they could.

487
00:47:52.173 --> 00:47:55.568
they violated then
existing industry standards

488
00:47:55.611 --> 00:47:57.744
for the production of herbicides

489
00:47:57.787 --> 00:48:01.487
by using a process
that was much shorter.

490
00:48:01.530 --> 00:48:03.358
at higher temperatures.

491
00:48:03.402 --> 00:48:07.362
that was responsible for
the presence of the dioxin

492
00:48:07.406 --> 00:48:12.411
in the ultimate chemical
substances that were created.

493
00:48:14.108 --> 00:48:15.588
